ntly only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/slot\"><code>&lt;slot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/source\"><code>&lt;source&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"nonStdElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/spacer\"><code>&lt;spacer&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard obsolete\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Veraltet:</strong> Dieses Feature ist veraltet. Obwohl es in manchen Browsern immer noch funktioniert, wird von seiner Benutzung abgeraten, da es jederzeit entfernt werden kann. Es sollte daher nicht mehr verwendet werden.</p></div></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zusammenfassung","title":"Zusammenfassung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das HTML Teletype (Fernschreiber) Text Element (<code>&lt;tt&gt;</code>) erzeugt ein inline Element das in der standardmässigen Nichtproportionalschrift des Browsers angezeigt wird. Die Absicht hinter diesem Element war, Text so zu präsentieren, als würde er auf einem Bildschirm mit fester Breite angezeigt, wie bei einem Fernschreiber. Es ist vermutlich verbreiteter, Text mit fester Breite mit dem Element <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/code\"><code>&lt;code&gt;</code></a> anzuzeigen.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">Dieses Element ist überholt. An seiner Stelle sollte ein angepasstes Element wie Beispielsweise <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/code\"><code>&lt;code&gt;</code></a> oder <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> mit <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/CSS\" title=\"/fr/docs/CSS\">CSS</a> benutzt werden.</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribute","title":"Attribute","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Element hat keine anderen Attribute als die <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\" title=\"HTML/global attributes\">globalen Attribute</a>, die alle Elemente verwenden.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dom_interface","title":"DOM Interface","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Element implementiert das <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Interface.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect4\">\n<p><strong>Anmerkung zur Implementation: </strong>Bis und mit Gecko 1.9.2, Firefox implementiert das <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Interface für dieses Element.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Geben Sie bei der Eingabeaufforderung des Fernschreibers folgendes Kommando ein: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>set localecho<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n\nDer Fernschreiber Client sollte <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>tt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Local Echo is on<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>tt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> anzeigen<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resultat","title":"Resultat","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Geben Sie bei der Eingabeaufforderung des Fernschreibers folgendes Kommando ein: <code>set localecho</code><br>\n Der Fernschreiber Client sollte: <code>Local Echo is on</code> anzeigen</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Anmerkungen","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Eine CSS-Regel kann für den <code>tt</code> Selektor definiert werden, um die Standardschriftart des Browsers anzupassen. Benutzereinstellungen können Vorrang vor dem spezifizierten CSS haben.</li>\n <li>Obwohl dieses Element nicht für deprecated erklärt wurde, wird mit der HTML 4.01 Spezification davon abgeraten es zu benutzen, stattdessen sollten Style Sheets (CSS) verwendet werden.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/code\"><code>&lt;code&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li>HTML 4.01 Spezifikation: <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html4/present/graphics.html#h-15.2\" rel=\" noopener\">Schriftstile</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"sect5\"></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Zusammenfassung","id":"zusammenfassung"},{"text":"Attribute","id":"attribute"},{"text":"DOM Interface","id":"dom_interface"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Anmerkungen","id":"notes"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Das HTML Teletype (Fernschreiber) Text Element (<tt>) erzeugt ein inline Element das in der standardmässigen Nichtproportionalschrift des Browsers angezeigt wird. Die Absicht hinter diesem Element war, Text so zu präsentieren, als würde er auf einem Bildschirm mit fester Breite angezeigt, wie bei einem Fernschreiber. Es ist vermutlich verbreiteter, Text mit fester Breite mit dem Element <code> anzuzeigen.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<tt>: The Teletype Text element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"tt","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<tt> : l'élément de texte de téléscripteur (obsolète)","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<tt>: テレタイプテキスト要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"tt","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"<tt>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/html/element/tt","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/html/element/tt/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: HyperText Markup Language"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt","title":"<tt>"}],"pageTitle":"<tt> - HTML: HyperText Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}